  - [ ] Cross-store analytics
  
- [ ] **Advanced Automation**
  - [ ] Auto-pricing based on competition
  - [ ] Dynamic profit margins
  - [ ] Automated product descriptions (AI)
  - [ ] Bulk actions (price updates, stock sync)
  
- [ ] **Order Fulfillment**
  - [ ] Direct order placement to suppliers
  - [ ] Shipping tracking integration
  - [ ] Returns management
  - [ ] Automated dropshipping workflow
  
- [ ] **GraphQL API**
  - [ ] Modern query language support
  - [ ] Real-time subscriptions
