## ğŸ’° Monetization Strategy (Future)

**Core Principle**: Keep the platform free forever. Revenue from value-added services.

### Free Forever
- âœ… Open-source codebase (MIT license)
- âœ… Basic product database access
- âœ… WordPress plugin
- âœ… API access (rate-limited)
- âœ… Community support

### Premium Services (Planned - Phase 3+)
- ğŸ’ **Pro Plan** ($29/month)
  - Higher API rate limits
  - Priority support
  - Advanced analytics
  - Early access to new features
  
- ğŸ’ **Enterprise Plan** ($299/month)
  - Unlimited API calls
  - Dedicated account manager
  - Custom integrations
  - White-label options
  - SLA guarantees
  
- ğŸ’ **Value-Added Services**
  - Premium WordPress themes ($49-199 one-time)
  - Professional product photography
  - Store setup service
  - Marketing consultation

### Revenue Sharing
- **Core Contributors**: 10% of premium revenue
- **Community Fund**: 5% for events, hackathons, bounties
- **Platform Development**: 85% for infrastructure, team, R&D

